Ernst & Young Buys Quindiem That Operates in Africa, Business Day Reports

-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 
2011-06-29T05:59:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-29/ernst-young-buys-quindiem-that-operates-in-africa-business-day-reports.html
Ernst & Young LLP bought Quindiem,
an actuarial science company with operations in  Kenya ,  Nigeria ,
Botswana and  Ghana , Business Day reported, citing Alex Thomson,
an actuarial leader at Quindiem.  The acquisition was for an undisclosed amount, the
Johannesburg-based newspaper cited Ernst & Young Chief Executive
Officer for Africa Ajen Sita as saying.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ana Monteiro at 
 amonteiro4@bloomberg.net  